OpenIDForm Nette component
======================

Description
-----------
This component allows you to add the OpenID authentication to your Nette-powered
application. It is based on the LightOpenID library, see
http://gitorious.org/lightopenid for more info.

Requirements
------------
Nette Framework 1.x or higher. (PHP 5.3 edition)
PHP curl extension enabled

Demo application
----------------
Repository includes a demo application, to make it work please set the
permissions of /temp, /log and /app/models/sql to 777 and permissions of
/app/models/sql/demo.db to 666
